    • ChEmedEprMedicationRequestChangedPml

      public ChEmedEprMedicationRequestChangedPml(ChEmedEprMedicationRequestPml request)
      Constructor that copies the content of the PML med request to a PML changed request. This is used as a workaround due to the limitations of HAPI's parser that will only parse all the medication requests to a single type. This method allows a custom parser (or other) to create a ChEmedEprMedicationRequestChangedPml by copying the values from a parsed ChEmedEprMedicationRequestPml request.

      If the passed medication request has the parentDocument extension (as it should if it passed validation), it will be part of the extensions (and not recognized as parentDocument by the ChEmedEprMedicationRequestChangedPml class, since the URLs differ). This constructor will move it from the extensions to the parentDocument custom property of this class.

      Parameters:
      request - The PML simple request.
